" pre-batched to match the shifted circuit instances. Specifically, if the"
" status tensor has shape [2, size, ...], the first slice [0, size, ...] "
"is used for the positive shifts and the second slice [1, size, ...] is "
"used for the negative shifts. If the status tensor has shape [size, ...],"
