"`out_edges` (`in_edges`) of `A.copy()` with that of `B.copy()`: "
"`new_out_edges = [*out_edges_A_copy, *out_edges_B_copy]` `new_in_edges = "
"[*in_edges_A_copy, *in_edges_B_copy]`"
