"Jz). Defaults to 1.0."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.heisenberg_hamiltonian:14
msgid ""
"Defines the range of interactions. - \"neighbors\": Includes only "
"nearest-neighbor pairs (default). - \"all\": Includes all unique pairs of"
" sites."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.heisenberg_hamiltonian:18
#: tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:28
msgid "The Hamiltonian as a backend-agnostic sparse matrix."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:1
msgid "Generates the sparse matrix of the Rydberg atom array Hamiltonian."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:3
msgid "The Hamiltonian is defined as: .. math::"
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:6
#, python-brace-format
msgid "H = \\sum_i \\frac{\\Omega}{2} X_i"
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:7
#, python-brace-format
msgid "\\sum_i \\frac{\\delta}{2} \\bigl(1 - Z_i \\bigr)"
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:8
msgid "\\sum_{i<j} \\frac{V_{ij}}{4} \\bigl(1 - Z_i \\bigr)\\bigl(1 - Z_j \\bigr)"
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:10
#, python-brace-format
msgid "= \\sum_i \\frac{\\Omega}{2} X_i"
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:11
#, python-brace-format
msgid "\\sum_i \\frac{\\delta}{2} Z_i"
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:12
msgid "\\sum_{i<j} \\frac{V_{ij}}{4}\\,\\bigl(Z_i Z_j - Z_i - Z_j \\bigr)"
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:14
#, python-brace-format
msgid "where :math:`V_{ij} = C6 / |r_i - r_j|^6`."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:16
msgid ""
"Note: Constant energy offset terms (proportional to the identity "
"operator) are ignored in this implementation."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:19
msgid ""
"An instance of a class derived from AbstractLattice, which provides site "
"coordinates and the distance matrix."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:22
msgid "The Rabi frequency (Î©) of the driving laser field."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:24
msgid "The laser detuning (Î´)."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.hamiltonians.rydberg_hamiltonian:26
msgid "The Van der Waals interaction coefficient (C6)."
msgstr ""

