"This class defines the common interface for all lattice structures, "
"providing access to fundamental properties like site information (count, "
"coordinates, identifiers) and neighbor relationships. Subclasses are "
"responsible for implementing the specific logic for generating the "
"lattice points and calculating neighbor connections."
msgstr ""

