#: of tensorcircuit.templates.lattice.AbstractLattice.get_all_pairs:1
msgid "Returns a list of all unique pairs of site indices (i, j) where i < j."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.lattice.AbstractLattice.get_all_pairs:3
msgid ""
"This method provides all-to-all connectivity, useful for Hamiltonians "
"where every site interacts with every other site."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.lattice.AbstractLattice.get_all_pairs:6
msgid ""
"Note on Differentiability: This method provides a static list of index "
"pairs and is not differentiable itself. However, it is designed to be "
"used in combination with the fully differentiable ``distance_matrix`` "
"property. By using the pairs from this method to index into the "
"``distance_matrix``, one can construct differentiable objective functions"
" based on all-pair interactions, effectively bypassing the non-"
"differentiable ``get_neighbor_pairs`` method for geometry optimization "
"tasks."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.lattice.AbstractLattice.get_all_pairs:14
msgid "A list of tuples, where each tuple is a unique pair of site indices."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.lattice.AbstractLattice.get_coordinates:1
