"Specifies which order of neighbor bonds to draw (e.g., 1 for NN, 2 for "
"NNN). If None, no bonds are drawn. If the specified neighbors have not "
"been calculated, a warning is printed. Defaults to None."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.lattice.AbstractLattice.show:17
msgid ""
"An existing Matplotlib Axes object to plot on. If None, a new Figure and "
"Axes are created automatically. Defaults to None."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.lattice.AbstractLattice.show:20
msgid ""
"A dictionary of keyword arguments for customizing bond appearance, passed"
" directly to the Matplotlib plot function. Defaults to None."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.lattice.AbstractLattice.show:24
msgid ""
"Additional keyword arguments to be passed directly to the "
"`matplotlib.pyplot.scatter` function for customizing site appearance."
msgstr ""

#: of tensorcircuit.templates.lattice.AbstractLattice.sites:1
