#: of tensorcircuit.templates.lattice.TILattice:19
msgid ""
"The Cartesian coordinates of the basis sites within the unit cell. Shape:"
" (num_basis_sites, dimensionality). For a simple Bravais lattice, this "
"would be `np.array([[0, 0]])`."
